---
import ProjectItem from "./Projects/ProjectItem.astro";
const futureDate = new Date();
futureDate.setFullYear(futureDate.getFullYear() + 10);

// TO BE CONFIRMED
const respondDate = new Date("2024-02-28");
const eventDate = new Date("2024-03-15");
---

<section class="flex justify-center px-8 py-8 pb-24">
  <div
    class="flex max-w-[1000px] grow flex-col space-y-10 rounded-lg border-2 border-accent bg-primary-bg px-16 py-12 text-sm text-white shadow-[16px_16px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] sm:text-lg"
  >
    <!-- ----------------------------- Letterhead ------------------------------ -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="text-right drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_#FF5DA9]">
        <p>
          {
            futureDate.toLocaleDateString(undefined, {
              year: "numeric",
              month: "long",
              day: "numeric",
            })
          }
        </p>
        <p>
          {Math.round((respondDate.valueOf() - Date.now()) / (24 * 60 * 60 * 1000))} days
          to respond
        </p>
        <p>
          {Math.round((eventDate.valueOf() - Date.now()) / (24 * 60 * 60 * 1000))} days
          until event
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- --------------------------- Letter Contents --------------------------- -->
      <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-10">
        <p class="text-lg font-bold italic drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_#FF5DA9] sm:text-2xl">
          Greetings, hacker.
        </p>
        <p>
          I hope you and your loved ones are well. It’s scary how fast the “zombie virus”
          has spread across the world.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our cities have turned to battlefields. Our subways and schools have grown
          infected with the fallen.
        </p>
        <p class="font-bold italic">It could be the beginning of the end.</p>
        <p>
          But technology still stands. WiFi is up, electricity runs, and hardware
          operates.
        </p>
        <p class="font-bold italic">We need your help.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-center py-8">
      <div class="flex max-w-[900px] grow flex-col space-y-6 text-center text-white">
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-2xl">
          Join <span class="font-bold text-accent">150 hackers</span> like you for
          <span class="font-bold text-accent2">42 hours</span> at our safehouse.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-white drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_#FF5DA9] sm:text-2xl">
          Build something, <span class="italic">anything</span>, to help us survive this
          apocalypse.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
